This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection and analysis of different object proposal methods. It may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it involves the evaluation of different methods and their impact on detector performance. Additionally, it may belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category as it involves the analysis of recall rates for ground truth annotations. Finally, it may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with image analysis and object detection.
